{"tid":846891,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"搭的士比錢四捨五入？","createTime":"2018-10-03T18:05:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T18:45:46.000Z","uid":180212,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dd46c5beae9c0b24b3ce90b6da9bd798709483b4","tid":846891,"uid":180212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T18:05:02.000Z","msg":"岩岩搭的士搭左$100.3<br />\n心諗銀包有張$100岩岩好 直程完美<br />\n點知個司機㩒停咗個表之後又冇出聲 睥住我<br />\n係呢個電光火石嘅moment 我就決定比張$100佢<br />\n我一開車門嘅時候 佢話<br />\n其實你係咪唔識睇數字 你搭咗$100.3喎 冇錢唔好學人搭的士<br />\n我個心係 屌你老母你又唔講收幾錢<br />\n然後佢又咁撚串 條氣真係好唔順<br />\n所以我就講 屌好明顯我就掙三毫子啦 你又唔係四捨五入計 點解你覺得我係爭一蚊 <br />\n最後我俾咗三亳子佢就落咗車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b5f47f0c3fa6490dba68bcd5f2ff85284b497e","tid":846891,"uid":24368,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T18:07:55.000Z","msg":"咁點解你唔俾埋個三毫子佢？"},{"pid":"793e563377819133ef1bcf7685df7a439f224b98","tid":846891,"uid":54736,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T18:08:06.000Z","msg":"平時啲毫子就收你一蚊，呢家收少三毫就咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3ecef92b70c0108090ea7aa585bf2e2fdf4119","tid":846891,"uid":24368,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98b5f47f0c3fa6490dba68bcd5f2ff85284b497e","tid":846891,"uid":24368,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T18:07:55.000Z","msg":"咁點解你唔俾埋個三毫子佢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T18:08:13.000Z","msg":"一開始"},{"pid":"3b8c608de059f89c6bdb202bcf498cf4f9fb5666","tid":846891,"uid":207192,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T18:19:12.000Z","msg":"睇你遇上邊個司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我之前由上水搭去西貢碼頭<br />\n個標係$223.X <br />\n個司機收我$230<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話齊頭好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nRound up至十位數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"h